"1  (2-lb.) block sharp Cheddar cheese, shredded","1  small onion, minced","2  garlic cloves, minced","1/2 teaspoon hot sauce","1/4 teaspoon ground red pepper","1  (12-oz.) bottle amber beer, at room temperature","  Salt and pepper to taste","  Garnish: thyme sprig"